{"tid":1537323,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"跟隊！富士山做文宣！光復香港時代革命","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T06:19:33.000Z","uid":68777,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f0584fc13886997bf28b495be483521d9b799c3","tid":1537323,"uid":68777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ckcOzf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ckcOzf.jpg&h=45bcacf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁多位，3個月黎辛苦喇，無論如何都唔好放棄，黑暗過後就會見到光明。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"c0648ef141d4f5bfe6eaf6853dda90dcd33a5e71","tid":1537323,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8W7Cuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8W7Cuk.jpg&h=a399d20e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"bec8554781b810b05890a25600bbb713d59dc59c","tid":1537323,"uid":134061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c86d3402e40f64a45cce05c133722bdbb01d559","tid":1537323,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:41:21.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3FYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=42477457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8806b1a27e98399aaa0895cbe08343cff0de585","tid":1537323,"uid":299258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f0584fc13886997bf28b495be483521d9b799c3","tid":1537323,"uid":68777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ckcOzf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ckcOzf.jpg&h=45bcacf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁多位，3個月黎辛苦喇，無論如何都唔好放棄，黑暗過後就會見到光明。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64749d8457f05567e6311275df8aec85f0a0ef11","tid":1537323,"uid":189377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"我遲啲都要去旅行 想問巴係咪人手整咖？定可以印 我手殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab56636c09781b717958f023cbb18e24fe83853b","tid":1537323,"uid":68777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64749d8457f05567e6311275df8aec85f0a0ef11","tid":1537323,"uid":189377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"我遲啲都要去旅行 想問巴係咪人手整咖？定可以印 我手殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"我估有公司可以印，我自己係幾蚊買塊布，再print張紙cut走隻字放上塊布填色"},{"pid":"7befbdac7a36b17e07ea2073e1fd525f5249296b","t